snippet.title: Cascading Curls On Natural Hair| Beauty Collab | Tia Kirby
snippet.description:
This video is a collab with my curl friend Janae Mason featuring a "Cascading Curls On Natural Hair" swept to the side.  To achieve my version of this style I use Flexirods.  My styling products are Curls Gel-Les'c & Blueberry Bliss Control Paste.  Tools used are my Denman D3 Brush, Rat Tail Comb & my Boar Bristle Brush.
